# ${{APP_NAME}}

A Python project created with Code on the Go.

## Setup

```bash
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

## Run

```bash
python main.py
```

Or use the **Run app** action in the toolbar. Add dependencies to
`requirements.txt` and use **Install requirements**.

## Project Structure

```
${{APP_NAME}}/
  main.py            # Application entry point
  requirements.txt   # Dependencies
  README.md
```
